<div>
  <h2>License Servers</h2>
  <p>
    License Servers is where we collect data on usage. Fireworks only supports Flex License Manager license server at the momment. 
  </p>
  <ul class="thumbnails">
    <li class="span4">
      <div class="thumbnail">
